&lt;p&gt;The&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt; Senior Product Marketing Manager &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;is responsible for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt; meeting and exceeding business &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;objectives&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt; for a portfolio of products and programs within the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;Sustainable Revenue &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;business. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;Critical to the success of the role includes developing a deep understanding of Skyscanner’s audiences, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;business&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt; and product strategies, as part of the wider launch plans and roadmap.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;wbzude&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Responsibilities and Focus Areas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Develop and own the global product marcomms strategy for Skyscanner’s B2B products and services to deliver against key strategic priorities and established KPIs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Stand up and execute the global product marcomms strategy, including all lifecycle stages by working cross functionally with the commercial team, product team, and the wider B2B marcomms team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Own the go-to-market strategy for new B2B product feature launches to drive awareness, engagement and lead generation via multiple channels against specific KPIS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Craft and communicate the story and vision of B2B partnership opportunities on Skyscannerfor our Advertising solutions platform to a broad range of partners, to ensure that potential and existing partners understand the value of all parts of Skyscanner’s&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Execute a drumbeat of speaking engagements to drive product awareness and adoption &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; Develop full product lifecycle measurement framework ensuring robust tracking against strategic priorities.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
