&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;We are looking for a motivated Business&amp;nbsp;Data Analyst that is passionate about discovering what the data says&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;has&amp;nbsp;a strong&amp;nbsp;business&amp;nbsp;sense. As a subject matter expert,&amp;nbsp;you will draw from your practical experience to produce highest quality data analysis, business insights and recommendations to be used by the business to inform decision making and guide strategy for business optimisation and growth. To do this you will act as the dedicated analytics partner within a business team using your skills to interpret large volumes of data across a wide and varied range of sources including Google Analytics, Tableau and our internal databases.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;This is an individual contributor role without direct reports. You will report to the Business Data Analyst Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a&amp;nbsp;Business&amp;nbsp;Data&amp;nbsp;Analyst&amp;nbsp;you:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are deeply numerate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Will thrive in the world where data, code, analytical methods and business overlap. When you are not crunching data you are spotting trends and sharing actionable insights&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excel at articulating and communicating analytical conclusions to team members and stakeholders at all levels of the business&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate and influence using data, producing convincing business cases and recommendations to your stakeholders&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pride yourself in earning the trust of your team members, stakeholders and internal customers through the consistent quality and contribution of your analysis, interpretation and guidance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upskill your colleagues enabling the wider team to be self-sufficient in performing analysis and deep dives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience you can bring:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Demonstrable track record delivering high quality analysis by distilling large and varied data sources to produce actionable business&amp;nbsp;insight&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;2&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience of applying analytical methods and techniques to deliver reliable&amp;nbsp;conclusions &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;3&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Using analytical tools such as Excel, Tableau, or equivalent&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience of using SQL&amp;nbsp;for accessing and manipulating&amp;nbsp;data&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Working effectively as contributing and guiding member of a team&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;6&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Ability to proactively manage and prioritise workload in a deadline driven&amp;nbsp;environment&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;7&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Owning projects and driving for successful business outcomes based on agreed metrics/KPIs&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;8&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;First class English written and verbal communication&amp;nbsp;skills&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;9&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Working experience in either a business/management or analytical role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally, you’ll also bring the following experience, but they are not must haves:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;10&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Creation&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;timely&amp;nbsp;production&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;high&amp;nbsp;quality&amp;nbsp;reports&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;dashboards&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;11&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;wrangling&amp;nbsp;multiple&amp;nbsp;datasets&amp;nbsp;to&amp;nbsp;deliver&amp;nbsp;actionable&amp;nbsp;insights&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;12&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;App/Web&amp;nbsp;analytics&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;consumer&amp;nbsp;internet sector&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;13&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;of&amp;nbsp;Python&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;data&amp;nbsp;analysis&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;14&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;web-based&amp;nbsp;platform&amp;nbsp;for&amp;nbsp;working&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;Spark&amp;nbsp;such&amp;nbsp;as&amp;nbsp;Databricks&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;5&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;15&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Experience of applying statistics in a business context&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#LI-C1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Every day, millions of people search for their perfect flight, hotel or rental car on Skyscanner! Our team is responsible for delivering data science solutions that power data-driven products across all these verticals and experimentation is a key part of this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Data Science Advertising team plays an important role in supporting Skyscanner&#39;s sustainable business model. We are responsible for helping our partners reach millions of people, using powerful ads to help them on this journey!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are turning our global data into significant insights and recommendations: helping airlines run more profitably, airports find new customers, and destination and marketing agencies understand demand. As a Senior Data Scientist you will work with cross-functional teams of Engineers, Product and Commercial Managers to drive our advertising and data product forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contributing to scoping, defining and prototyping new data products, and improving existing ones.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performing statistical analyses and build machine learning solutions to support Skyscanner product and business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building, deploying and maintaining ML models in production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Researching new ways of modelling data for actionable insights and product improvements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing and evaluating thorough experiments to generate findings and measure the effectiveness of our products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Some of our expectations for the role include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience working as a Data Scientist or ML engineer in the advertising space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years experience working in a Data Science role.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re comfortable with Python and Spark&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud platforms and software development tools (AWS/GCP/Azure, Git, Docker, CI/CD)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good data querying skills using variations of SQL dialects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience communicating effectively with both technical and non-technical colleagues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a user-centric mentality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy delivering in a dynamic environment with teammates from a variety of teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing multiple stakeholders and priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are happy to work mostly independently and ask for help when needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively look to evangelize Data Science across Skyscanner, efficiently collaborating with others to identify and scope out new opportunities for data science work to positively impact our product and vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where you’ll be:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This role can be in London, Glasgow, Edinburgh or Barcelona&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What else can we offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Every day, millions of people search for their perfect flight, hotel or rental car on Skyscanner! Our team is responsible for delivering data science solutions that power data-driven products across all these verticals and experimentation is a key part of this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Data Science marketing team plays a fundamental role in Skyscanner&#39;s sustainable growth and user base retention. We work on projects including bidding optimisation, personalising our communications, assessing incrementality, and supporting marketing with experimentation best practices. As a Data Scientist, you will join a multi-disciplinary team to help us quantify the ability of different marketing channels and strategies to bring awareness of our compelling travel content to travellers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applying classical statistical models and machine learning techniques to create scalable solutions for predictive learning or forecasting - what is our predicted 1 year ROI for different campaigns?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploying and maintaining models in production environments. What model metrics are important to track? When should we refresh our clustering or forecasting models?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing agile and rigorous experiments to measure efficiency of models, tools and programs. Knowing when to apply and how to design user-cohort A/B tests or geo-split / quasi-experimentation tests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recommending ways to optimise campaign efficiency and maximise profitable growth - how should we setup our Google AdWords campaigns?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentoring other team members and act as a subject matter expert of applied data science to marketing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnering closely with product, engineering, and marketing to tackle quantitative problems and identify trends and opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Some of our expectations for the role include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are curious and inquisitive. It&#39;s just not about the modelling, it&#39;s about the quality of the data, the business metrics, how the systems interact with each other and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have practical expertise in experimentation design and analysis. Bonus points for practical expertise on experimentation for non-user driven testing (marketing, quasi-experimentation and equivalent) and attribution/incremental testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Practical experience with Data Science applied to marketing - Measuring efficiency of campaigns across multiple channels, recency-frequency modelling, evaluating multi-touch attribution, media mix modelling etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience proactively building stakeholder relationships and an active interest in mentoring and developing others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience with Google AdWords and Google Analytics or other digital data tools. How to setup our keywords PPC campaigns and ad groups? How to optimise bids and budgets?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong statistical and classical machine learning modelling basis (regression, classification, clustering).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are comfortable working with large datasets and proficient in tools such as SQL, Python, R, Spark.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have a good understanding of software development tools (Git, PyCharm, Docker, CI/CD, AWS (or equivalent)).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can communicate clearly with both technical and non-technical colleagues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 5+ years experience working in a Data Science role.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What else can we offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;/p&gt;

