&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focused. Supportive. Honest.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kubernetes, Docker, Python, Java, and AWS – you’ll be up to speed with at least three of them, and keen to build your knowledge on them all! In Production Platform tribe, we leverage software to do systems at scale! You will join a set of teams who build and operate a core technology platform for product teams to run their services across the globe. This includes large scale Kubernetes clusters, core AWS/web infrastructure, operational monitoring, core libraries, CI/CD, and developer tools. We strive to provide a powerful and resilient base that enables other Engineers to focus on delivering outstanding features to our travellers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a skilled Software Engineer your sound tech experience of Agile/Lean methodologies will be vital for continuous improvement. And though the customer rules your world, your team’s important too. You always help colleagues perform at their best and turn big solutions into smaller, bite-sized tasks.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Most roles at Skyscanner can be either Full Time or Part Time. We need your expertise to help us do something great for our travellers: make booking stays and journeys more sustainable and straightforward. It involves technical challenges and the latest technology, from machine learning and cloud services to world-class APIs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a Software Engineer, you’ll help us develop a whole range of key product features in your area. It involves defining and implementing services that make up a vital sub-system. As you work, you’ll collaborate across other product engineering development lifecycles, learning and influencing. Alongside being accountable for your own projects, you&#39;ll form part of a broader team that takes collective responsibility for making success happen.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;For more details on Engineering at Skyscanner, check our &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/@Skyscannereng&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Engineering Blog&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SkyscannerEng&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Skyscanner Engineering&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;on Twitter.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;#LI-JG1&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Swift, Objective-C, UIKit, SwiftUI, Core Animation, Core Data, Combine, Cocoapods / Swift Package manager, Webkit, Mapkit, Cuckoo, XCTest – as a skilled software engineer, you’re experienced in some and curious about the rest. Whatever your technical abilities, you’ll be adept at developing, releasing and maintaining native apps. You’ll base your decisions on metrics and use agile/lean methodologies. You’ll also know that delivery is all about balancing technical, analytical and product needs, and that big tasks need to be broken down. This isn’t just about having great technical talents, though. We’re also looking for a sense of team spirit, dedication to customers and accountability for your own projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As a Mobile Engineer, you’ll work on native app development. It’s all about building and shipping features from the ground up. You’ll be accountable for designing, building and running your features in production, that means system design, monitoring how it’s being used, and making data driven decisions on how to evolve features. You’ll have a varied role with plenty of learning opportunities. Right now, we’re building some kickass tooling, with deploy pipelines out of the box, state of the art experimentation tools, and an awesome inter-team collaboration set-up. If you want responsibility for multiple product feature components, this is where you need to be.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Though you’ll be accountable for your own projects and trusted to deliver, you’ll also form part of a broader team that takes collective responsibility for making success happen.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Travel is back! Skyscanner’s unwavering commitment to our travellers and partners remains as strong as ever. We are on a mission to make travel more sustainable and straightforward, and we’ll need your expertise to help all the new considerations of an ever evolving industry.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, health screenings, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;For more details on Engineering at Skyscanner, check our &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/@Skyscannereng&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Engineering Blog&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; and follow &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SkyscannerEng&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Skyscanner Engineering&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; on Twitter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Focused. Supportive. Honest.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kubernetes, Docker, Python, Java, and AWS – you’ll be up to speed with at least three of them, and keen to build your knowledge on them all! In Production Platform tribe, we leverage software to do systems at scale! You will join a set of teams who build and operate a core technology platform for product teams to run their services across the globe. This includes large scale Kubernetes clusters, core AWS/web infrastructure, operational monitoring, core libraries, CI/CD, and developer tools. We strive to provide a powerful and resilient base that enables other Engineers to focus on delivering outstanding features to our travellers.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a skilled Software Engineer your sound tech experience of Agile/Lean methodologies will be vital for continuous improvement. And though the customer rules your world, your team’s important too. You always help colleagues perform at their best and turn big solutions into smaller, bite-sized tasks.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Most roles at Skyscanner can be either Full Time or Part Time. We need your expertise to help us do something great for our travellers: make booking stays and journeys more sustainable and straightforward. It involves technical challenges and the latest technology, from machine learning and cloud services to world-class APIs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a Software Engineer, you’ll help us develop a whole range of key product features in your area. It involves defining and implementing services that make up a vital sub-system. As you work, you’ll collaborate across other product engineering development lifecycles, learning and influencing. Alongside being accountable for your own projects, you&#39;ll form part of a broader team that takes collective responsibility for making success happen.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;For more details on Engineering at Skyscanner, check our &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/@Skyscannereng&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Engineering Blog&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;and follow&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SkyscannerEng&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Skyscanner Engineering&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;on Twitter.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;#LI-JG1&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Innovative. Brave. Straightforward. At Skyscanner, we like to keep things simple. Working here involves collaboration, ownership and bags of innovation. We’re not afraid to admit that it’s different from the norm. But if you’re our kind of Graduate, you’ll feel right at home.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;The opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are looking for Engineering Graduates who have a passion for innovation and eagerness to learn new technologies. We operate small, empowered teams who use industry leading technologies and work in sprints to deliver value. Our engineers are constantly innovating and thrive on new challenges, and you&#39;ll have opportunities to gain experience and exposure to different technologies through regular rotations. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Whether you want to build and improve the engine that powers Skyscanner across all platforms, focus on providing the best user interface on all devices, create innovative technologies to support our growth, or even &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;all&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; of the above, we want to hear from you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Programme duration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; 24 months&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Number of rotations: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;You will take part in 4 rotations – spending 6 months working across several areas such as Backend, Frontend, Mobile, Data and Product&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; . &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;10&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;In addition to the rotational element of the scheme, there may be international placements, dependent on business need.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Location: Shenzhen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Start date: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;4 September 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Why choose us:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We have lots of experience nurturing fresh talent at Skyscanner and some of our senior leaders started in Early Careers when they first joined years ago. We want to do everything possible to help you develop on a personal and professional level. We have a supportive, trusting and transparent working environment; a place where you can look at things differently, to challenge and offer solutions. Within the program you will go through four rotations. This gives you the unique opportunity to work in different areas of the business. Our programme is an opportunity to learn, master and develop your craft in a community of experienced engineering mentors. We are&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;a data-centric culture, with a strong focus on experimentation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; You&#39;ll get experience across different tech stacks, platforms, products, frontend, backend, app, data and more!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;What are we looking for:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;A successfully completed Bachelors or Masters degree in the field of Software Engineering / Computer Science (or on track to be completed by September 2023)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;A good strong technical foundation with the potential to achieve technical excellence&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Passion and curiosity for the technology industry which extends beyond your academic studies &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Commitment to developing your technical and personal skills &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;Ability to collaborate both in your team and across the business &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;A fresh perspective and willingness to share ideas and do things differently &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;7&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;You must obtain work authorisation in the country of employment at the time of hire, and maintain ongoing work authorisation during employment &lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Recruitment Process:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Want to join us? Please submit your CV and cover letter below. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Ideally you will need to be available to attend our Discovery Day in person in our Edinburgh office (&amp;nbsp;we will reimburse up to £150 towards travel costs). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;9&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;1&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;If you meet the description above, we will send you an online coding test created by our engineers.  This will give you an idea of some real life Skyscanner problems. You will have 7 days to complete this test &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;9&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;2&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;If you pass the coding test, you may be progressed to the second stage which is a Zoom interview with our Early Careers Lead&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;9&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559684&amp;quot;:-2,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Symbol&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469769242&amp;quot;:[8226],&amp;quot;469777803&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;left&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777804&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;469777815&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;hybridMultilevel&amp;quot;}&quot; data-aria-posinset=&quot;3&quot; data-aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;If the interview is successful, we will invite you to a Discovery Day in our Edinburgh office&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:1080,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:259}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;You must have or obtain the right to work in the country of employment at the time of hire and maintain that right to work throughout the Graduate Programme&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt; . &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Where visa sponsorship opportunities are available, these can be discussed with you if required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About this role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Travel. It’s one of life’s simple pleasures. But, ooof, planning it can feel like hard work. For the last 18 years we’ve been on a mission to empower every traveller with innovative tools, insights and experiences that help people get to where they’re going, so they can spend more time out exploring the world, and less time anxiously bouncing around 25 browser tabs and endless spreadsheets. Our traveller-first approach drives everything we do and it’s never been more important than it is today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Being part of Skyscanner means joining a team hell bent on building the world’s most innovative, and helpful travel experiences possible. We’re hugely ambitious and believe we have the chance to genuinely challenge and disrupt the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do you always stay innovative and open-mind with a progressive mindset to challenge systems and provide solutions to change?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How to use appropriate architecture and frameworks to tackle the technical challenges from large scale long term projects？&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are you passionate about the Agile development process and improving the efficiency of software creation?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are you passionate about delivering quality results at the end of each development cycle?&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven Kotlin,&amp;nbsp;Java&amp;nbsp;development experience with apps published to the app store.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with Fastlane, AWS, Dagger, Kotlin Coroutines, RxJava, Retrofit, Android Architecture Components,&amp;nbsp;you’re experienced in some and curious about the rest.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good understanding of development methodologies, testing practices, and tools and knowing when to apply them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoying in a community of great and enthusiastic people who share goals and accomplishments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience applying software design and architectural patterns and knowing the benefits and trade-off between them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills and willingness to ask for help and bounce ideas and solutions off peers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor degree or above in computer science or a related technical discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5 years of React Native App dev experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience of solving one or more large scale problems.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with App performance tuning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong learning ability, can quickly understand the business model and business needs of industry clients in a short period of time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent organization, prioritization, cross-team collaboration and communication skills.
&lt;p id=&quot;AndroidAppEngineer-Nicetohave:&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have :&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in online travel industry or search engines is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in leading highly-complex, technically-challenging, cross-functional software oriented projects is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java language&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Proficient in Kotlin&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;native build tools, like XCode and Android Studio&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;REST APIs in a mobile context，AWS experience is&amp;nbsp;a major plus&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Other Native programming languages like Swift is nice to have&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some full stack experience working with backend like Nodejs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead or guidance Junior engineers in the team and help them grow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, code and maintain mobile user experiences end-to-end for Android platforms in our Accommodations and Cars Tribe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize code for performance, stability and maintainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diagnose and fix bugs and performance bottlenecks for performance that feels native&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reach out to the open source community to encourage and help implement mission-critical software fixes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write automated unit tests to ensure the product is of the highest quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with a cross-functional team of UX Designers, Product Managers and other developers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;DataEngineerJobDescription-JobOverview&quot;&gt;Job Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Sr. Data Engineer to join our accommodation and car hire data team. The hire will be &lt;strong&gt;responsible for expanding and optimizing our data and data pipeline architecture, as well as optimizing data flow and collection for cross functional teams&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Data Engineer will support our software developers, database architects, data analysts and data scientists on data initiatives and will ensure optimal data delivery architecture is consistent throughout ongoing projects. They must be self-directed and comfortable supporting the data needs of multiple teams, systems and products. The right candidate will be excited by the prospect of optimizing or even re-designing our company’s data architecture to support our next generation of products and data initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;DataEngineerJobDescription-ResponsibilitiesforDataEngineer&quot;&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain optimal data pipeline architecture,&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assemble large, complex data sets that meet functional / non-functional business requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, design, and implement internal process improvements: automating manual processes, optimizing data delivery, re-designing infrastructure for greater scalability, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the infrastructure required for optimal extraction, transformation, and loading of data from a wide variety of data sources using SQL and AWS ‘big data’ technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build analytics tools that utilize the data pipeline to provide actionable insights into customer acquisition, operational efficiency and other key business performance metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with stakeholders including the Executive, Product, Data and Design teams to assist with data-related technical issues and support their data infrastructure needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create data tools for analytics and data scientist team members that assist them in building and optimizing our product into an innovative industry leader.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with data and analytics experts to strive for greater functionality in our data systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;DataEngineerJobDescription-QualificationsforDataEngineer&quot;&gt;Qualifications for Data Engineer&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java, Python, Docker and AWS - you will master at least two of them and be keen to build your knowledge on them&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with relational SQL and NoSQL databases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Relevant work experience with big data tools: Hadoop, Spark, Kafka, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have a strong thirst for knowledge, and maintain the exploration and enthusiasm for new technologies&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have English reading and writing skills, able to meet the reading and writing needs of daily work&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with data pipeline and workflow management tools is preferred&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with AWS cloud services (EC2, EMR, RDS, Redshift) is preferred&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Every day, millions of people search for their perfect flight, hotel or rental car on Skyscanner! &amp;nbsp;Our team is responsible for delivering data science solutions that power data-driven products across all these verticals. Our goal is to ensure travellers receive highly relevant and personalised experiences that are optimised and scalable. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a skilled Sr. Data Scientist, you will be responsible for delivering high impact projects related to data and modelling across a broad range of topics. You will own the full lifecycle of your project, including the discovery of business opportunities, supporting collection of our traveller and business data as well as the feature transformations and engineering with the development and monitoring of machine learning models. Since our models reach millions of travellers, you will be responsible for developing simple and scalable solutions at the highest standards. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Scientists at Skyscanner are working on exciting projects such as hotel and flights ranking, recommendation of destinations, price prediction, product inventory optimisation across 1000+ partners, among many other data rich projects. You can expect to formulate ideas, develop prototypes and work with engineers to implement models in live production systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role will include:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;1&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Lead a small (growing) team of Data Scientists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;1&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Liaise with senior stakeholders across a key area of the business to define and prioritise the Data Science roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Research new ways of modelling data for actionable insights and product improvements for our hotel offerings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform statistical analyses and build machine learning solutions to support Skyscanner hotels product&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with product and engineering to solve quantitative problems and identify trends and opportunities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design agile and rigorous experiments to measure&amp;nbsp;effectiveness&amp;nbsp;of models, tools and&amp;nbsp;programs&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy and maintain models in production environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Some of our expectations for the role include: &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;1&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience coaching/mentoring junior data scientists&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can communicate clearly with both technical and non-technical colleagues. You accurately judge the level of detail required in different situations.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have extensive experience developing statistical and machine learning models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience with end to end model productionisation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;1&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You have worked 5+ years in a data science role,&amp;nbsp; with experience in a senior/lead position&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’re comfortable with Python and/or R&amp;nbsp;(Spark helpful as well)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have&amp;nbsp;good&amp;nbsp;data querying skills using variations of&amp;nbsp;SQL dialects (Hive,&amp;nbsp;SparkSql, Athena)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience of cloud platforms and software development tools (AWS/GCP/Azure, Git, Docker, CI/CD)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy working in a dynamic environment with teammates from a variety of disciplines. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can manage multiple stakeholders and priorities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can communicate effectively in a global team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are happy to work&amp;nbsp;mostly independently and ask for help when needed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively look to&amp;nbsp;evangelize&amp;nbsp;Data Science across the Skyscanner. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What else can we offer you……&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skyscanner’s unwavering dedication to our travellers and partners remains as strong as ever. We’re confident that our travellers’ appetite to explore the world will return, and we are excited to navigate the new considerations of an evolving industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Already a global leader in travel, we want to elevate the way we work to a whole other level. In return, you’ll get meaningful things like medical insurance, health screenings, headspace subscriptions, a home office allowance and the option to buy more holiday. You’ll have the opportunity to work from any country for 4 weeks a year, and 30 days in our other global offices. You also have the option to take part in our extended annual leave which is an additional 3 weeks’ break (unpaid) after 3 years’ service and take 5 weeks’ break (paid) after 5 years’ service.&amp;nbsp;Everything, in other words, to help you relax and give your best.&lt;/p&gt;

